title: Amy Wants To Vacation Under A Rock + Raymundo’s Fiancé Gets A Touching Wedding Gift + Caitlyn Smith Performs In Studio
itunes:title: Amy Wants To Vacation Under A Rock + Raymundo’s Fiancé Gets A Touching Wedding Gift + Caitlyn Smith Performs In Studio
description:
Amy shares why she wants to take a new vacation ‘under a rock’. Raymundo is getting married this weekend and tells us about a very personal wedding gift his fiancé received. Plus, Caitlyn Smith stops by and performs a song from her new deluxe album. She shares the stories behind the songs she wrote for Garth Brooks, Trisha Yearwood and Dolly + Kenny!
